ERO - Ekobyarnas Riksorganisation Vision and Mission ERO strives:
- to promote ecological living and sustainable lifestyles in community, with others, in the city and the countryside;
- to strengthen people's opportunities to carry out an ecological adaptation of their construction and living;
to  create interest for ecological living and sustainable ways of life in community with others in both contact with societies various bodies, businesses and networks as well as mass media and membership fees;
to connect existing ecovillages, and to share info and possibilities of project applications, education and courses. 
