GEN-Russia Vision and Mission Participants of the Union regardless of their confession believe that sustainable live on our planet depends on the realization of the following principles:
- Environmental care, preservation and recovery of natural biodiversity as absolute priority of any human activity on Earth;
- Principle of conscious minimalism coming up to replace the philosophy of unrestrained, constantly growing consumerism;
- Aspiration to the personal development;
