Red Ibérica de Ecoaldeas (RIE) Vision and Mission In November 2001, the Founding Assembly of the Iberian Network of Ecovillages was held in Madrid. From then until today our basic objectives are: 
1) The exchange of information and resources between members of the network, and other people or groups;
2)The dissemination of the concept of ecovillage and sustainable settlement;
3) To facilitate the approach of people who, from towns and cities, wish to bet on these ways of life. About The Iberian Network of Ecovillages is the network that relates, connects and brings together different Ecovillages that are operating in the Iberian Peninsula, different Ecovillage projects that are wanting to be created and different associations with similar objectives. To the people who are living, search...
